{
  "text": "The above formulations provide the initial information for the drops that are introduced into the computational domain. The widely used TAB breakup model [CITATION_1] is chosen in the present study in order to estimate the secondary breakup of those droplets. The TAB model utilizes the analogy between a distorted droplet and an oscillating spring-mass-system. The force balance for the droplet gives ",
